export default ()=>`

Everything you need to know...and then some

  • Vendors and Buyers will NOT be charged a membership fee
  • For Vendors: All in One will take 5% off of every sale
  • Buyers will not be charged any premiums
  • All members intending to sell or buy will need an account with our bank app
  • Vendors & Buyers will be responsible to adhere to their state/local firearm laws
  • Venders will insure proper communication with consumer
  • Venders will take sole responsibility for insuring their product(s)
  • All gun purchases will need to go through a FLL
  • All In One (AIO) does not take responsibility for any lost packages
  • Members can escalate any issues to AIO if it cannot be resolved between the parties involved
  • Advertising with All In One will be charged depending on packet chosen by Vendor here
`
